{
  "stem": "8072.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember planes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And bombs-- not that much, because it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next thing I remember, the German army marching in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German army marching in, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No-- not myself at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I got to that camp-- like I didn't finish-- I had some bread with me, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I found out that I was-- my brother was there, so I went-- I don't know how-- I don't know exactly-- but I went to bring him some bread.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I got back to where the horse and buggy was there to go back to our town, the other two or three people that we were almost like in a caravan, they had left because they couldn't wait for me, because they had to get back before the curfew was up.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was getting-- so when I got back to-- the horse was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The buggy was a little late.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was trying to go as fast as the horse could go to get back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the other people got back, I remember my mom or something, they said, where's Moishe?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where's Moishe?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, well, we didn't see him when we got back to go back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The horse was there and the buggy was there, so I got the probably just in the nick and the wood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were worried, scared what happened to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was only 12 years old, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was right after the war had broken out?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
